These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
House: cape-cod, craftsman, colonial
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, ambient, salsa
1. the fan of ambient is in the middle##1
2. the colonial house is the fan of salsa##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| House   | cape-cod | craftsman | colonial   |
| Music-Genre      | hip-hop    | ambient  | salsa |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, aconite, rose
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, snooker
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
2. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
3. the person playing poker is the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Flower      | aconite | tulip     | rose      |
| Game   | poker | mah-jongg | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, tram, trike
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, soccer, baseball
1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Transport   | taxi | trike  | tram       |
| Sport       | cycling     | soccer | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, mystery
House: tower, wooden, townhouse
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the townhouse house##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the tower house##1
3. the townhouse house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Movie-Genre    | mystery    | comedy     | animation |
| House   | townhouse | tower | wooden     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, banana, peach
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, baccarat, havana
1. the baccarat-smoker is the person eating peach##1
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
3. the person eating peach is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
4. the person eating lettuce is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Food         | banana | lettuce     | peach |
| Cigar   | havana        | pall-mall | baccarat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, prince, davidoff
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, camping, traveling
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Cigar        | davidoff | fonseca      | prince  |
| Hobby   | writing       | camping | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
