.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, pakistani, mexican
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, boat, motorbike
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the american##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the pakistani is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality    | mexican | american | pakistani      |
| Transport   | bus     | motorbike | boat |

