The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, software-developer, dancer
1. the manager is the person traveling to rome##1
2. the software-developer is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| City   | paris | rome | london  |
| Job     | dancer     | manager      | software-developer |

