.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, snowboarding, skateboarding
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, kale, cauliflower
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the far right##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Sport      | soccer   | snowboarding    | skateboarding    |
| Food   | kale | blueberry | cauliflower |

