3 different pets are kept: goat, cat, chinchilla
1. the alhambra-smoker is the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the goat is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Cigar   | baccarat | alhambra   | swisher  |
| Pet   | chinchilla    | goat | cat |

