.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-12::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, motorbike, boat
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
1. the person driving the quad-bike is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Transport   | boat    | quad-bike     | motorbike   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda | hot-chocolate |

