2. the person traveling to hamburg is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| City   | new-york     | hamburg   | paris     |
| Pet    | guinea-pig | snake | rabbit |

