.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, january, april
3 different games are played: go, canasta, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Birthday   | june    | april | january |
| Game   | poker | go     | canasta        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, june
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, malaysian, canadian
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
2. the canadian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Birthday      | july  | june | april  |
| Nationality   | malaysian | canadian   | colombian |

