.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, chess
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, golf, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Hobby   | singing | puzzles | chess    |
| Sport        | basketball    | volleyball | golf |

