.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia, ebony
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, snake, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Color           | fuchsia | ebony | light-blue |
| Pet   | mouse  | guinea-pig      | snake |

